{"timestamp":1782133684507,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"threadlocal","blocks":[{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":11,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>ThreadLocal</code> 的作用是让每个线程拥有一份独立变量副本，避免多个线程共享同一个变量。常见场景包括用户上下文、链路追踪traceId、数据库连接等。</p>"},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":61,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Thread\n-&gt; ThreadLocalMap\n-&gt; Entry(ThreadLocal 弱引用, value 强引用)\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">Thread\n-&"},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":11,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>它并不是把数据存在 <code>ThreadLocal</code> 对象里，而是存在当前线程的 <code>ThreadLocalMap</code> 中，<code>ThreadLocal</code> 只是访问这个 Map 的 key。</p>"},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":82,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"try {\n    context.set(userId);\n    // business\n} finally {\n    context.remove();\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted="},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>所以使用原则很简单：谁设置，谁清理；线程池、Web 请求拦截器、异步任务尤其要放在 <code>finally</code> 中调用 <code>remove()</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
