{"timestamp":1782133684511,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"virtual-threads","blocks":[{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程是 JDK 21 正式引入的轻量级线程，属于 Project Loom 的核心能力。它仍然是 <code>java.lang.Thread</code>，但不再一一绑定操作系统线程，而是由 JDK 调度到少量平台线程上执行。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 Virtual Thread -&gt; 少量 Platform Thread -&gt; OS Thread\"><code>传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 V"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":94,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程不是让 CPU 密集型计算变快。CPU 计算仍然受核心数限制，如果任务一直占用 CPU，虚拟线程再多也只是增加调度压力。它真正改善的是阻塞 IO 场景下平台线程被长时间占住的问题。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":85,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用时还要注意 synchronized 临界区、阻塞 native 调用、连接池容量等限制。虚拟线程能让线程更便宜，但数据库连接、下游服务吞吐和限流策略仍然要单独设计。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782133684511,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"virtual-threads","before":[{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程是 JDK 21 正式引入的轻量级线程，属于 Project Loom 的核心能力。它仍然是 <code>java.lang.Thread</code>，但不再一一绑定操作系统线程，而是由 JDK 调度到少量平台线程上执行。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 Virtual Thread -&gt; 少量 Platform Thread -&gt; OS Thread\"><code>传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 V"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":94,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程不是让 CPU 密集型计算变快。CPU 计算仍然受核心数限制，如果任务一直占用 CPU，虚拟线程再多也只是增加调度压力。它真正改善的是阻塞 IO 场景下平台线程被长时间占住的问题。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":85,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用时还要注意 synchronized 临界区、阻塞 native 调用、连接池容量等限制。虚拟线程能让线程更便宜，但数据库连接、下游服务吞吐和限流策略仍然要单独设计。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程是 JDK 21 正式引入的轻量级线程，属于 Project Loom 的核心能力。它仍然是 <code>java.lang.Thread</code>，但不再一一绑定操作系统线程，而是由 JDK 调度到少量平台线程上执行。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 Virtual Thread -&gt; 少量 Platform Thread -&gt; OS Thread\"><code class=\"\">传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":94,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程不是让 CPU 密集型计算变快。CPU 计算仍然受核心数限制，如果任务一直占用 CPU，虚拟线程再多也只是增加调度压力。它真正改善的是阻塞 IO 场景下平台线程被长时间占住的问题。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":85,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用时还要注意 synchronized 临界区、阻塞 native 调用、连接池容量等限制。虚拟线程能让线程更便宜，但数据库连接、下游服务吞吐和限流策略仍然要单独设计。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782133684512,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"pattern-matching","blocks":[{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Pattern Matching 解决的是“先<span class=\"em-warn\">判断类型</span>，再强<span class=\"em-warn\">制转换</span>，再<span class=\"em-warn\">定义变量</span>”这类重复代码。它把类型判断、类型转换和局部变量绑定合在一起，让分支逻辑更清晰。</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":68,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String s) {\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span cl"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>传统写法需要先 <code>instanceof</code> 判断，再手动强转：</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":95,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String) {\n    String s = (String) obj;\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":81,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试可以这样说：<mark>Pattern Matching 不只是语法糖</mark>，它让 Java 在处理多态数据、协议对象、表达式树、领域事件时更容易写出类型安全且可读的分支代码。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782133684513,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"pattern-matching","before":[{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Pattern Matching 解决的是“先<span class=\"em-warn\">判断类型</span>，再强<span class=\"em-warn\">制转换</span>，再<span class=\"em-warn\">定义变量</span>”这类重复代码。它把类型判断、类型转换和局部变量绑定合在一起，让分支逻辑更清晰。</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":68,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String s) {\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span cl"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>传统写法需要先 <code>instanceof</code> 判断，再手动强转：</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":95,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String) {\n    String s = (String) obj;\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":81,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试可以这样说：<mark>Pattern Matching 不只是语法糖</mark>，它让 Java 在处理多态数据、协议对象、表达式树、领域事件时更容易写出类型安全且可读的分支代码。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Pattern Matching 解决的是“先<span class=\"em-warn\">判断类型</span>，再强<span class=\"em-warn\">制转换</span>，再<span class=\"em-warn\">定义变量</span>”这类重复代码。它把类型判断、类型转换和局部变量绑定合在一起，让分支逻辑更清晰。</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":68,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String s) {\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">if (obj insta"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>传统写法需要先 <code>instanceof</code> 判断，再手动强转：</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":95,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String) {\n    String s = (String) obj;\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-high"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":81,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试可以这样说：<mark>Pattern Matching 不只是语法糖</mark>，它让 Java 在处理多态数据、协议对象、表达式树、领域事件时更容易写出类型安全且可读的分支代码。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782133684513,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"minor-vs-full-gc","blocks":[{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 和 Full GC 的区别主要在回收范围、触发原因和停顿成本。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 通常<span class=\"em-warn\">回收年轻代</span>，Full GC 往往会回收<span class=\"em-warn\">整个堆</span>以及相关元数据区域，<strong>停顿更重</strong>。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":89,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存活对象进入 Survivor 或晋升老年代\n-&gt; 老年代压力过大\n-&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code>新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":33,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>频繁 Minor GC 不一定是严重问题，但会增加 CPU 消耗；</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">频繁 Full GC 通常是明显风险信号</span>，需要结合 GC 日志、<code>jstat</code>、heap dump 和对象分配链路排查。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>GC日志：</mark>GC频率、 GC停顿时间、 GC前后堆大小变化</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":34,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>jstat：</mark>YongGC FullGC 次数 、老年代 元空间使用率</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":35,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>heap dump：</mark>具体对象内存占用和引用 、异常大的Map List</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782133684514,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-jdk-jre","blocks":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp hljs","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782133684513,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"minor-vs-full-gc","before":[{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 和 Full GC 的区别主要在回收范围、触发原因和停顿成本。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 通常<span class=\"em-warn\">回收年轻代</span>，Full GC 往往会回收<span class=\"em-warn\">整个堆</span>以及相关元数据区域，<strong>停顿更重</strong>。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":89,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存活对象进入 Survivor 或晋升老年代\n-&gt; 老年代压力过大\n-&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code>新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":33,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>频繁 Minor GC 不一定是严重问题，但会增加 CPU 消耗；</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">频繁 Full GC 通常是明显风险信号</span>，需要结合 GC 日志、<code>jstat</code>、heap dump 和对象分配链路排查。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>GC日志：</mark>GC频率、 GC停顿时间、 GC前后堆大小变化</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":34,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>jstat：</mark>YongGC FullGC 次数 、老年代 元空间使用率</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":35,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>heap dump：</mark>具体对象内存占用和引用 、异常大的Map List</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 和 Full GC 的区别主要在回收范围、触发原因和停顿成本。</p>"},{"label":