{"timestamp":1782133684520,"sessionId":"5803c5","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:after-normalize","message":"DOM after normalize","data":{"innerHTML":"\n        <p>Java 先通过 javac 编译成字节码，运行时 JVM 可以解释执行字节码，也可以把热点代码 JIT 编译成本地机器码，因此是编译与解释并存。</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li>编译阶段把源码转换成平台无关字节码，便于分发和校验。</li>\n          <li>解释执行让程序可以快速启动并保持动态能力。</li>\n          <li>JIT 根据运行时 profiling 信息优化热点路径，例如方法内联、逃逸分析、锁消除。</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p>GraalVM Native Image ：构建时提前把 Java 应用编译成本地可执行文件。</p>\n      ","childTags":["P:","UL:","P:"]},"hypothesisId":"C","runId":"post-fix-2"}
{"timestamp":1782133684523,"sessionId":"5803c5","location":"html-serializer.js:serializeSection","message":"Section node analysis","data":{"elementChildCount":3,"blockTags":["<p>Java 先通过 javac 编译成字节码，运行时 JVM 可以解释执行字","<ul>\n          <li>编译阶段把源码转换成平台无关字节码，便于分","<p>GraalVM Native Image ：构建时提前把 Java 应用编"],"hasGraalVM":true},"hypothesisId":"B,G","runId":"post-fix-2"}
{"timestamp":1782133684527,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:after-serialize","message":"serialized section with code","data":{"sectionId":"Java-mul-thread","hasPre":true,"hasLanguageJava":true,"pCodeCount":4,"snippet":"Callable</code> 和 <code>Runnable</code> 类似，也是定义任务，但它可以返回结果</p>\n        <p><code>CompletableFuture</code> 是 Java 8 引入的异步编程工具。它不仅能异步执行任务，还能进行链式调用、任务组合、结果转换</p>\n        <pre><code class=\"language-java\">import java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture;\n\npublic class CompletableFutureDemo {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        CompletableFuture&lt;Integer&gt; future = CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(() -&gt; {\n            System.out.println(&quot;异步执行任务：&quot; + Thread."},"hypothesisId":"B,C","runId":"post-fix"}
