{"timestamp":1782133784763,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"thread-pool-flow","blocks":[{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":51,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>线程池提交任务后，不是直接无限创建线程，而是按照核心线程、任务队列、最大线程、拒绝策略的顺序控制资源。</p>"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满：创建非核心线程\n-&gt; 线程达到最大值且队列仍满：执行拒绝策略\"><code>提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>排查线程池问题时，重点看活跃线程数、队列长度、拒绝次数、任务耗时和下游阻塞情况。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
