{"timestamp":1782134376659,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"reactor-model","blocks":[{"label":"reactor-model","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":57,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Reactor 模型是一种事件驱动网络模型，由事件多路复用器监听 IO 事件，再分发给对应 Handler 处理。</p>"},{"label":"reactor-model","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":65,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Selector 监听 IO 事件\n-&gt; 事件就绪\n-&gt; 分发给 Handler\n-&gt; Handler 处理读写、编解码或业务任务\"><code class=\"\">Selector 监听 IO 事件\n-&gt; 事件就绪\n-&gt; 分发给 Handler\n-&gt; Handler 处理读写"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
