{"timestamp":1782134595178,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:after-serialize","message":"serialized section with code","data":{"sectionId":"sync-async-block-nonblock","hasPre":false,"hasLanguageJava":false,"pCodeCount":0,"snippet":"阻塞读</td></tr>\n            <tr><td>异步</td><td>调用方发起后，由回调、Future、事件通知处理结果</td><td>CompletableFuture、异步回调</td></tr>\n            <tr><td>阻塞</td><td>等待期间线程被挂起，不能做别的事</td><td>BIO read</td></tr>\n            <tr><td>非阻塞</td><td>调用立即返回，线程可以继续处理其它任务</td><td>NIO non-blocking channel</td></tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n        <p>同步不一定阻塞，异步也不等于一定更快。它们描述的是不同维度：同步/异步看结果获取方式，阻塞/非阻塞看等待时线程状态。</p>\n      </section>"},"hypothesisId":"B,C","runId":"post-fix"}
