t":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>从一组根对象 GC Roots 出发，沿引用链向下搜索；</p>"},{"label":"gc-roots","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":26,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>能够被搜索到的对象是可达的，不可达对象才可能被回收。</p>"},{"label":"gc-roots","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>注意“不可达”不等于立刻回收。对象如果重写了 <code>finalize()</code>，历史版本中还可能经历一次终结机会；</p>"},{"label":"gc-roots","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":18,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>现代 Java 中不推荐依赖 finalize，资源释放应使用 <code>try-with-resources</code> 或显式关闭。</p>"},{"label":"gc-roots","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":31,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JNI&nbsp;（Java Native Interface）作用是：</p>"},{"label":"gc-roots","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":46,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>&nbsp; Java 代码&nbsp; -&gt;&nbsp; JNI&nbsp; -&gt;&nbsp; C/C++ 代码 （操作系统 图像音频处理）</p>"},{"label":"gc-roots","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":205,"newlineCount":11,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"public class HelloJNI {\n\n    static {\n        System.loadLibrary(&quot;hello&quot;);\n    }\n\n    public native void sayHello();\n\n    public static void main("},{"label":"gc-roots","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":1,"newlineCount":1,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134610325,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"virtual-threads","blocks":[{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程是 JDK 21 正式引入的轻量级线程，属于 Project Loom 的核心能力。它仍然是 <code>java.lang.Thread</code>，但不再一一绑定操作系统线程，而是由 JDK 调度到少量平台线程上执行。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 Virtual Thread -&gt; 少量 Platform Thread -&gt; OS Thread\"><code>传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 V"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":94,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程不是让 CPU 密集型计算变快。CPU 计算仍然受核心数限制，如果任务一直占用 CPU，虚拟线程再多也只是增加调度压力。它真正改善的是阻塞 IO 场景下平台线程被长时间占住的问题。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":85,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用时还要注意 synchronized 临界区、阻塞 native 调用、连接池容量等限制。虚拟线程能让线程更便宜，但数据库连接、下游服务吞吐和限流策略仍然要单独设计。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134610325,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"virtual-threads","before":[{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程是 JDK 21 正式引入的轻量级线程，属于 Project Loom 的核心能力。它仍然是 <code>java.lang.Thread</code>，但不再一一绑定操作系统线程，而是由 JDK 调度到少量平台线程上执行。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 Virtual Thread -&gt; 少量 Platform Thread -&gt; OS Thread\"><code>传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 V"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":94,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程不是让 CPU 密集型计算变快。CPU 计算仍然受核心数限制，如果任务一直占用 CPU，虚拟线程再多也只是增加调度压力。它真正改善的是阻塞 IO 场景下平台线程被长时间占住的问题。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":85,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用时还要注意 synchronized 临界区、阻塞 native 调用、连接池容量等限制。虚拟线程能让线程更便宜，但数据库连接、下游服务吞吐和限流策略仍然要单独设计。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程是 JDK 21 正式引入的轻量级线程，属于 Project Loom 的核心能力。它仍然是 <code>java.lang.Thread</code>，但不再一一绑定操作系统线程，而是由 JDK 调度到少量平台线程上执行。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚拟线程：\n大量 Virtual Thread -&gt; 少量 Platform Thread -&gt; OS Thread\"><code class=\"\">传统平台线程：\nJava Thread -&gt; OS Thread\n\n虚"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":94,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>虚拟线程不是让 CPU 密集型计算变快。CPU 计算仍然受核心数限制，如果任务一直占用 CPU，虚拟线程再多也只是增加调度压力。它真正改善的是阻塞 IO 场景下平台线程被长时间占住的问题。</p>"},{"label":"virtual-threads","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":85,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用时还要注意 synchronized 临界区、阻塞 native 调用、连接池容量等限制。虚拟线程能让线程更便宜，但数据库连接、下游服务吞吐和限流策略仍然要单独设计。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134610326,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"pattern-matching","blocks":[{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Pattern Matching 解决的是“先<span class=\"em-warn\">判断类型</span>，再强<span class=\"em-warn\">制转换</span>，再<span class=\"em-warn\">定义变量</span>”这类重复代码。它把类型判断、类型转换和局部变量绑定合在一起，让分支逻辑更清晰。</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":68,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String s) {\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span cl"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>传统写法需要先 <code>instanceof</code> 判断，再手动强转：</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":95,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String) {\n    String s = (String) obj;\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":81,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试可以这样说：<mark>Pattern Matching 不只是语法糖</mark>，它让 Java 在处理多态数据、协议对象、表达式树、领域事件时更容易写出类型安全且可读的分支代码。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
