"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 通常<span class=\"em-warn\">回收年轻代</span>，Full GC 往往会回收<span class=\"em-warn\">整个堆</span>以及相关元数据区域，<strong>停顿更重</strong>。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":89,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存活对象进入 Survivor 或晋升老年代\n-&gt; 老年代压力过大\n-&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code class=\"\">新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor G"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":33,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>频繁 Minor GC 不一定是严重问题，但会增加 CPU 消耗；</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">频繁 Full GC 通常是明显风险信号</span>，需要结合 GC 日志、<code>jstat</code>、heap dump 和对象分配链路排查。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>GC日志：</mark>GC频率、 GC停顿时间、 GC前后堆大小变化</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":34,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>jstat：</mark>YongGC FullGC 次数 、老年代 元空间使用率</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":35,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>heap dump：</mark>具体对象内存占用和引用 、异常大的Map List</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134619629,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-jdk-jre","blocks":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp hljs","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134619629,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-jdk-jre","before":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp hljs","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}],"final":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134619630,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"wrapper-cache","blocks":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134619630,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"wrapper-cache","before":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134619631,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"generics-erasure","blocks":[{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":67,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Java 泛型用于在编译期提供类型约束，减少强制类型转换和运行时类型错误。类型擦除指大部分泛型信息在编译后被擦除为原始类型或边界类型。</p>"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":86,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">List&lt;String&gt; names = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ArrayList</span>&lt;&gt;();\nnames.add(<spa"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":61,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>泛型的价值主要在编译期类型安全。运行期如果需要完整泛型信息，通常要借助匿名子类、反射 Type 或框架提供的类型引用对象。</p>"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":86,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>List&lt;String&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\nlist.add(\"hello\");\n\nString value = list.get(0);</code></p>"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":0,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p></p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134620962,"sessionId":"5803c5","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-normalize","message":"DOM before normalize","data":{"innerHTML":"\n        <p>Java 先通过 javac 编译成字节码，运行时 JVM 可以解释执行字节码，也可以把热点代码 JIT 编译成本地机器码，因此是编译与解释并存。</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li>编译阶段把源码转换成平台无关字节码，便于分发和校验。</li>\n          <li>解释执行让程序可以快速启动并保持动态能力。</li>\n          <li>JIT 根据运行时 profiling 信息优化热点路径，例如方法内联、逃逸分析、锁消除。</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p>GraalVM Native Image ：构建时提前把 Java 应用编译成本地可执行文件。</p>\n      ","childTags":["P:","UL:","P:"],"childNodes":["#text:","P:","#text:","UL:","#text:","P:","#text:"],"textContent":"\n        Java 先通过 javac 编译成字节码，运行时 JVM 可以解释执行字节码，也可以把热点代码 JIT 编译成本地机器码，因此是编译与解释并存。\n        \n          编译阶段把源码转换成平台无关字节码，便于分发和校验。\n          解释执行让程序可以快速启动并保持动态能力。\n          JIT 根据运行时 profiling 信息优化热点路径，例如方法内联、逃逸分析、锁消除。\n        \n        GraalVM Native Image ：构建时提前把 Java 应用编译成本地可执行文件。\n      "},"hypothesisId":"B,C,F,G","runId":"post-fix-2"}
{"timestamp":1782134620963,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-memory","blocks":[{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":51,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"线程共享：\n- 堆\n- 方法区 / 元空间\n\n线程私有：\n- 虚拟机栈\n- 本地方法栈\n- 程序计数器\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">线程共享：\n- 堆\n- 方法区 / 元空间\n\n线程"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":18,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">存放对象实例</span>，是垃圾回收的主要区域。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":23,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"User user = new User();\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">User</span> <span class=\"hljs"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":61,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>存放类信息、常量、静态变量、方法元数据等。JDK 8 之后，方法区的实现主要是 Metaspace 元空间，使用本地内存。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>每个线程私有。每次方法调用都会创建一个栈帧，包含局部变量表、操作数栈、方法返回地址、动态链接等。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
