ewlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"User user = new User();\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">User user = new User();</code></pre>"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":61,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>存放类信息、常量、静态变量、方法元数据等。JDK 8 之后，方法区的实现主要是 Metaspace 元空间，使用本地内存。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>每个线程私有。每次方法调用都会创建一个栈帧，包含局部变量表、操作数栈、方法返回地址、动态链接等。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134620963,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-heap","blocks":[{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":17,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM 堆通常分为年轻代和老年代。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":20,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>新对象大多数先进入年轻代。年轻代又分为：</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":36,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Eden 区\nSurvivor From 区\nSurvivor To 区\"><code class=\"\">Eden 区\nSurvivor From 区\nSurvivor To 区</code></pre>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":73,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>对象一般先分配到 Eden 区。当年轻代空间不足时，会触发 Minor GC。存活下来的对象会进入 Survivor 区，多次存活后晋升到老年代。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":60,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>老年代存放生命周期较长的对象，例如长期存在的缓存对象、Spring 单例 Bean、大集合、多次 GC 后仍存活的对象。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":76,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象 -&gt; Eden\nMinor GC 后存活 -&gt; Survivor\n多次存活 -&gt; 老年代\n老年代不足 -&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code class=\"\">新对象 -&gt; Eden\nMinor GC 后存活 -&gt; Survivor\n多次存活 -&g"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134620964,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-heap","before":[{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":17,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM 堆通常分为年轻代和老年代。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":20,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>新对象大多数先进入年轻代。年轻代又分为：</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":36,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Eden 区\nSurvivor From 区\nSurvivor To 区\"><code class=\"\">Eden 区\nSurvivor From 区\nSurvivor To 区</code></pre>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":73,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>对象一般先分配到 Eden 区。当年轻代空间不足时，会触发 Minor GC。存活下来的对象会进入 Survivor 区，多次存活后晋升到老年代。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":60,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>老年代存放生命周期较长的对象，例如长期存在的缓存对象、Spring 单例 Bean、大集合、多次 GC 后仍存活的对象。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":76,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象 -&gt; Eden\nMinor GC 后存活 -&gt; Survivor\n多次存活 -&gt; 老年代\n老年代不足 -&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code class=\"\">新对象 -&gt; Eden\nMinor GC 后存活 -&gt; Survivor\n多次存活 -&g"}],"final":[{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":17,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM 堆通常分为年轻代和老年代。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":20,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>新对象大多数先进入年轻代。年轻代又分为：</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":36,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Eden 区\nSurvivor From 区\nSurvivor To 区\"><code class=\"\">Eden 区\nSurvivor From 区\nSurvivor To 区</code></pre>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":73,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>对象一般先分配到 Eden 区。当年轻代空间不足时，会触发 Minor GC。存活下来的对象会进入 Survivor 区，多次存活后晋升到老年代。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":60,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>老年代存放生命周期较长的对象，例如长期存在的缓存对象、Spring 单例 Bean、大集合、多次 GC 后仍存活的对象。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":76,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象 -&gt; Eden\nMinor GC 后存活 -&gt; Survivor\n多次存活 -&gt; 老年代\n老年代不足 -&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code class=\"\">新对象 -&gt; Eden\nMinor GC 后存活 -&gt; Survivor\n多次存活 -&g"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134620964,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"volatile","blocks":[{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>volatile</code> 是 Java 中的轻量级同步机制，主要解决变量在多线程之间的可见性和指令重排序问题。它适合状态标记、配置开关、单例双重检查等场景，但不能替代锁。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":25,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"保证可见性\n禁止指令重排序\n不保证复合操作的原子性\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">保证可见性\n禁止指令重排序\n不保证复合操作的原子性</code></pre>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>普通变量可能被线程缓存到工作内存中，一个线程修改后，另一个线程不一定立刻看到。<code>volatile</code> 会要求写入及时刷新到主内存，读取时从主内存获取最新值。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"private volatile boolean running = true;\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>这类写法常用于线程停止标记：一个线程把 <code>running</code> 改成 false，另一个循环线程能尽快感知。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>volatile</code> 会在读写前后加入内存屏障，限制编译器和 CPU 对相关指令进行危险重排。经典例子是双重检查单例，避免对象引用先暴露、构造尚未完成的问题。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":385,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"public class Singleton {\n    private static volatile Singleton instance;\n\n    private Singleton() {}\n\n    public static Singleton getInstance() {\n        if"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":32,"newlineCount":1,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"volatile int count = 0;\ncount++;\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">volatile</span> <"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>count++</code> 包含读取、加一、写回三个步骤，<code>volatile</code> 不能保证整体原子性。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134620965,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"volatile","before":[{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>volatile</code> 是 Java 中的轻量级同步机制，主要解决变量在多线程之间的可见性和指令重排序问题。它适合状态标记、配置开关、单例双重检查等场景，但不能替代锁。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":25,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"保证可见性\n禁止指令重排序\n不保证复合操作的原子性\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">保证可见性\n禁止指令重排序\n不保证复合操作的原子性</code></pre>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>普通变量可能被线程缓存到工作内存中，一个线程修改后，另一个线程不一定立刻看到。<code>volatile</code> 会要求写入及时刷新到主内存，读取时从主内存获取最新值。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"private volatile boolean running = true;\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>这类写法常用于线程停止标记：一个线程把 <code>running</code> 改成 false，另一个循环线程能尽快感知。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>volatile</code> 会在读写前后加入内存屏障，限制编译器和 CPU 对相关指令进行危险重排。经典例子是双重检查单例，避免对象引用先暴露、构造尚未完成的问题。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":385,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"public class Singleton {\n    private static volatile Singleton instance;\n\n    private Singleton() {}\n\n    public static Singleton getInstance() {\n        if"},{"label":"volatile","