ass 搬进 JVM，检查一下，准备静态变量，执行 static 初始化，然后就能用了</p>"},{"label":"class-loading","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":3,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>类初始化通常发生在首次主动使用时，例如 <code>new</code> 对象、访问静态字段、调用静态方法、反射调用等。</p>"},{"label":"class-loading","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">双亲委派模型 </span>可以避免核心类被重复或恶意替换，例如应用自定义的 <code>java.lang.String</code> 不应该覆盖 JDK 自带类。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134620972,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"parent-delegation","blocks":[{"label":"parent-delegation","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>双亲委派模型指类加载器加载类时，先把请求委派给父加载器，父加载器无法加载时，子加载器才尝试加载。</p>"},{"label":"parent-delegation","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp hljs","textLen":148,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"BootstrapClassLoader\n\n↑委托   ↓ 加载  \n\nExtClassLoader\n\n↑委托   ↓ 加载  \n\nAppClassLoader\n\n↑委托   ↓ 加载  \n\n自定义 ClassLoader  \n\n// 向上委托 向下加载\n// 父加载器找不到，子加载器才自己加载\" data-c"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
