tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":85,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用时还要注意 synchronized 临界区、阻塞 native 调用、连接池容量等限制。虚拟线程能让线程更便宜，但数据库连接、下游服务吞吐和限流策略仍然要单独设计。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134620975,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"pattern-matching","blocks":[{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Pattern Matching 解决的是“先<span class=\"em-warn\">判断类型</span>，再强<span class=\"em-warn\">制转换</span>，再<span class=\"em-warn\">定义变量</span>”这类重复代码。它把类型判断、类型转换和局部变量绑定合在一起，让分支逻辑更清晰。</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":68,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String s) {\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span cl"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>传统写法需要先 <code>instanceof</code> 判断，再手动强转：</p>"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":95,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"if (obj instanceof String) {\n    String s = (String) obj;\n    System.out.println(s.length());\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data"},{"label":"pattern-matching","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":81,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试可以这样说：<mark>Pattern Matching 不只是语法糖</mark>，它让 Java 在处理多态数据、协议对象、表达式树、领域事件时更容易写出类型安全且可读的分支代码。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
