{"timestamp":1782134896738,"sessionId":"5803c5","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-normalize","message":"DOM before normalize","data":{"innerHTML":"\n        <p>Java 先通过 javac 编译成字节码，运行时 JVM 可以解释执行字节码，也可以把热点代码 JIT 编译成本地机器码，因此是编译与解释并存。</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li>编译阶段把源码转换成平台无关字节码，便于分发和校验。</li>\n          <li>解释执行让程序可以快速启动并保持动态能力。</li>\n          <li>JIT 根据运行时 profiling 信息优化热点路径，例如方法内联、逃逸分析、锁消除。</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p>GraalVM Native Image ：构建时提前把 Java 应用编译成本地可执行文件。</p>\n      ","childTags":["P:","UL:","P:"],"childNodes":["#text:","P:","#text:","UL:","#text:","P:","#text:"],"textContent":"\n        Java 先通过 javac 编译成字节码，运行时 JVM 可以解释执行字节码，也可以把热点代码 JIT 编译成本地机器码，因此是编译与解释并存。\n        \n          编译阶段把源码转换成平台无关字节码，便于分发和校验。\n          解释执行让程序可以快速启动并保持动态能力。\n          JIT 根据运行时 profiling 信息优化热点路径，例如方法内联、逃逸分析、锁消除。\n        \n        GraalVM Native Image ：构建时提前把 Java 应用编译成本地可执行文件。\n      "},"hypothesisId":"B,C,F,G","runId":"post-fix-2"}
{"timestamp":1782134896738,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-memory","blocks":[{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":51,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"线程共享：\n- 堆\n- 方法区 / 元空间\n\n线程私有：\n- 虚拟机栈\n- 本地方法栈\n- 程序计数器\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">线程共享：\n- 堆\n- 方法区 / 元空间\n\n线程"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":18,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">存放对象实例</span>，是垃圾回收的主要区域。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":23,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"User user = new User();\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">User</span> <span class=\"hljs"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":61,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>存放类信息、常量、静态变量、方法元数据等。JDK 8 之后，方法区的实现主要是 Metaspace 元空间，使用本地内存。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>每个线程私有。每次方法调用都会创建一个栈帧，包含局部变量表、操作数栈、方法返回地址、动态链接等。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
