ewlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"User user = new User();\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">User user = new User();</code></pre>"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":61,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>存放类信息、常量、静态变量、方法元数据等。JDK 8 之后，方法区的实现主要是 Metaspace 元空间，使用本地内存。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-memory","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>每个线程私有。每次方法调用都会创建一个栈帧，包含局部变量表、操作数栈、方法返回地址、动态链接等。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134896740,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-heap","blocks":[{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":17,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM 堆通常分为年轻代和老年代。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":20,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>新对象大多数先进入年轻代。年轻代又分为：</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":36,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Eden 区\nSurvivor From 区\nSurvivor To 区\"><code>Eden 区\nSurvivor From 区\nSurvivor To 区</code></pre>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":73,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>对象一般先分配到 Eden 区。当年轻代空间不足时，会触发 Minor GC。存活下来的对象会进入 Survivor 区，多次存活后晋升到老年代。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":60,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>老年代存放生命周期较长的对象，例如长期存在的缓存对象、Spring 单例 Bean、大集合、多次 GC 后仍存活的对象。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-heap","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":76,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象 -&gt; Eden\nMinor GC 后存活 -&gt; Survivor\n多次存活 -&gt; 老年代\n老年代不足 -&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code>新对象 -&gt; Eden\nMinor GC 后存活 -&gt; Survivor\n多次存活 -&gt; 老年代\n老年"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
