{"timestamp":1782134912166,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"minor-vs-full-gc","blocks":[{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 和 Full GC 的区别主要在回收范围、触发原因和停顿成本。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 通常<span class=\"em-warn\">回收年轻代</span>，Full GC 往往会回收<span class=\"em-warn\">整个堆</span>以及相关元数据区域，<strong>停顿更重</strong>。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":89,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存活对象进入 Survivor 或晋升老年代\n-&gt; 老年代压力过大\n-&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code>新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":33,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>频繁 Minor GC 不一定是严重问题，但会增加 CPU 消耗；</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">频繁 Full GC 通常是明显风险信号</span>，需要结合 GC 日志、<code>jstat</code>、heap dump 和对象分配链路排查。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>GC日志：</mark>GC频率、 GC停顿时间、 GC前后堆大小变化</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":34,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>jstat：</mark>YongGC FullGC 次数 、老年代 元空间使用率</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":35,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>heap dump：</mark>具体对象内存占用和引用 、异常大的Map List</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782134912166,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"minor-vs-full-gc","before":[{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 和 Full GC 的区别主要在回收范围、触发原因和停顿成本。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":48,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 通常<span class=\"em-warn\">回收年轻代</span>，Full GC 往往会回收<span class=\"em-warn\">整个堆</span>以及相关元数据区域，<strong>停顿更重</strong>。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":89,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存活对象进入 Survivor 或晋升老年代\n-&gt; 老年代压力过大\n-&gt; Major GC / Full GC\"><code>新对象大量分配\n-&gt; Eden 不足\n-&gt; Minor GC\n-&gt; 存"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":33,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>频繁 Minor GC 不一定是严重问题，但会增加 CPU 消耗；</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">频繁 Full GC 通常是明显风险信号</span>，需要结合 GC 日志、<code>jstat</code>、heap dump 和对象分配链路排查。</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>GC日志：</mark>GC频率、 GC停顿时间、 GC前后堆大小变化</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":34,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>jstat：</mark>YongGC FullGC 次数 、老年代 元空间使用率</p>"},{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":35,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><mark>heap dump：</mark>具体对象内存占用和引用 、异常大的Map List</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"minor-vs-full-gc","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Minor GC 和 Full GC 的区别主要在回收范围、触发原因和停顿成本。</p>"},{"label":