{"timestamp":1782134912168,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"wrapper-cache","blocks":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
