{"timestamp":1782137552786,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"volatile","blocks":[{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>volatile</code> 是 Java 中的轻量级同步机制，主要解决变量在多线程之间的可见性和指令重排序问题。它适合状态标记、配置开关、单例双重检查等场景，但不能替代锁。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":25,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"保证可见性\n禁止指令重排序\n不保证复合操作的原子性\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">保证可见性\n禁止指令重排序\n不保证复合操作的原子性</code></pre>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>普通变量可能被线程缓存到工作内存中，一个线程修改后，另一个线程不一定立刻看到。<code>volatile</code> 会要求写入及时刷新到主内存，读取时从主内存获取最新值。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"private volatile boolean running = true;\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>这类写法常用于线程停止标记：一个线程把 <code>running</code> 改成 false，另一个循环线程能尽快感知。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>volatile</code> 会在读写前后加入内存屏障，限制编译器和 CPU 对相关指令进行危险重排。经典例子是双重检查单例，避免对象引用先暴露、构造尚未完成的问题。</p>"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":385,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"public class Singleton {\n    private static volatile Singleton instance;\n\n    private Singleton() {}\n\n    public static Singleton getInstance() {\n        if"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":32,"newlineCount":1,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"volatile int count = 0;\ncount++;\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">volatile</span> <"},{"label":"volatile","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>count++</code> 包含读取、加一、写回三个步骤，<code>volatile</code> 不能保证整体原子性。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137552787,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"locks","blocks":[{"label":"locks","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":12,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>synchronized</code> 和 <code>ReentrantLock</code> 都能实现互斥访问，并且都是可重入锁。区别在于：<code>synchronized</code> 是 JVM 关键字，写法简单、自动释放；<code>ReentrantLock</code> 是 JUC 工具类，功能更灵活，但必须手动释放。</p>"},{"label":"locks","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":49,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"\npublic synchronized void method() {\n    // 临界区\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\""},{"label":"locks","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":386,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"\nprivate final ReentrantLock lock = new ReentrantLock();\n\npublic void method() {\n    lock.lock();\n    try {\n        // 临界区\n    } finally {\n        lock.unlo"},{"label":"locks","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":12,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>一般优先使用 <code>synchronized</code>。需要尝试加锁、可中断锁、公平锁、多条件队列或复杂同步控制时，再使用 <code>ReentrantLock</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137552788,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"locks","before":[{"label":"locks","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":12,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>synchronized</code> 和 <code>ReentrantLock</code> 都能实现互斥访问，并且都是可重入锁。区别在于：<code>synchronized</code> 是 JVM 关键字，写法简单、自动释放；<code>ReentrantLock</code> 是 JUC 工具类，功能更灵活，但必须手动释放。</p>"},{"label":"locks","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":49,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"\npublic synchronized void method() {\n    // 临界区\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\""},{"label":"locks","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":386,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"\nprivate final ReentrantLock lock = new ReentrantLock();\n\npublic void method() {\n    lock.lock();\n    try {\n        // 临界区\n    } finally {\n        lock.unlo"},{"label":"locks","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":12,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>一般优先使用 <code>synchronized</code>。需要尝试加锁、可中断锁、公平锁、多条件队列或复杂同步控制时，再使用 <code>ReentrantLock</code>。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"locks","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":12,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>synchronized</code> 和 <code>ReentrantLock</code> 都能实现互斥访问，并且都是可重入锁。区别在于：<code>synchronized</code> 是 JVM 关键字，写法简单、自动释放；<code>ReentrantLock</code> 是 JUC 工具类，功能更灵活，但必须手动释放。</p>"},{"label":"locks","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":49,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"\npublic synchronized void method() {\n    // 临界区\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">\npublic synchronized void method"},{"label":"locks","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":386,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"\nprivate final ReentrantLock lock = new ReentrantLock();\n\npublic void method() {\n    lock.lock();\n    try {\n        // 临界区\n    } finally {\n        lock.unlo"},{"label":"locks","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":12,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>一般优先使用 <code>synchronized</code>。需要尝试加锁、可中断锁、公平锁、多条件队列或复杂同步控制时，再使用 <code>ReentrantLock</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137552788,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"proxy","blocks":[{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":115,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>代理模式是在不直接访问目标对象的情况下，通过代理对象间接访问目标对象，并在调用前后增强额外逻辑。Java 动态代理是在运行时生成代理对象，常见用途包括 AOP、日志、权限校验、事务管理、RPC、MyBatis Mapper 代理。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 动态代理要求目标类实现接口，底层通过 <code>Proxy</code> 和 <code>InvocationHandler</code> 拦截接口方法调用。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":42,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"interface UserService {\n    void save();\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">interfa"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":192,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"InvocationHandler handler = (proxy, method, args) -&gt; {\n    System.out.println(&quot;before&quot;);\n    Object result = method.invoke(target, args);\n    S"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>通过生成目标类的子类实现代理。不要求接口，但不能代理 <code>final</code> 类和 <code>final</code> 方法。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里可以补一句：Spring AOP 默认有接口时倾向使用 JDK 动态代理，没有接口时通常使用 CGLIB。动态代理解决的是“统一横切增强”的问题，不适合把复杂业务逻辑藏进代理层。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137552789,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"proxy","before":[{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":115,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>代理模式是在不直接访问目标对象的情况下，通过代理对象间接访问目标对象，并在调用前后增强额外逻辑。Java 动态代理是在运行时生成代理对象，常见用途包括 AOP、日志、权限校验、事务管理、RPC、MyBatis Mapper 代理。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 动态代理要求目标类实现接口，底层通过 <code>Proxy</code> 和 <code>InvocationHandler</code> 拦截接口方法调用。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":42,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"interface UserService {\n    void save();\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">interfa"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":192,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"InvocationHandler handler = (proxy, method, args) -&gt; {\n    System.out.println(&quot;before&quot;);\n    Object result = method.invoke(target, args);\n    S"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>通过生成目标类的子类实现代理。不要求接口，但不能代理 <code>final</code> 类和 <code>final</code> 方法。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里可以补一句：Spring AOP 默认有接口时倾向使用 JDK 动态代理，没有接口时通常使用 CGLIB。动态代理解决的是“统一横切增强”的问题，不适合把复杂业务逻辑藏进代理层。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":115,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>代理模式是在不直接访问目标对象的情况下，通过代理对象间接访问目标对象，并在调用前后增强额外逻辑。Java 动态代理是在运行时生成代理对象，常见用途包括 AOP、日志、权限校验、事务管理、RPC、MyBatis Mapper 代理。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 动态代理要求目标类实现接口，底层通过 <code>Proxy</code> 和 <code>InvocationHandler</code> 拦截接口方法调用。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":42,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"interface UserService {\n    void save();\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">interface UserService {\n    void save()"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":192,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"InvocationHandler handler = (proxy, method, args) -&gt; {\n    System.out.println(&quot;before&quot;);\n    Object result = method.invoke(target, args);\n    S"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>通过生成目标类的子类实现代理。不要求接口，但不能代理 <code>final</code> 类和 <code>final</code> 方法。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里可以补一句：Spring AOP 默认有接口时倾向使用 JDK 动态代理，没有接口时通常使用 CGLIB。动态代理解决的是“统一横切增强”的问题，不适合把复杂业务逻辑藏进代理层。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137552789,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"hashmap-principle","blocks":[{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>HashMap</code> 是基于数组、链表和红黑树实现的 key-value 容器。核心思路是先通过 key 的 <code>hashCode()</code> 计算哈希值，再定位到数组桶位；如果多个 key 落到同一个桶，就通过链表或红黑树解决哈希冲突。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":126,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"put 流程：\n计算 key 的 hash\n-&gt; 定位数组下标\n-&gt; 桶为空：直接放入\n-&gt; 桶不为空：比较 hash 和 equals\n-&gt; key 已存在：覆盖 value\n-&gt; key 不存在：追加到链表或红黑树\n-&gt; 元素数量超过阈值：触发扩容\"><code>put "},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":78,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 8 之后，桶内元素较少时使用链表；当链表长度达到阈值且数组容量足够大时，会转成红黑树，把极端冲突下的查询复杂度从 O(n) 降到 O(log n)。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：自定义对象作为 key 时必须正确重写 <code>equals()</code> 和 <code>hashCode()</code>；<code>HashMap</code> 本身不是线程安全的，并发写入要使用外部锁或并发容器。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137552789,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"hashmap-principle","before":[{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>HashMap</code> 是基于数组、链表和红黑树实现的 key-value 容器。核心思路是先通过 key 的 <code>hashCode()</code> 计算哈希值，再定位到数组桶位；如果多个 key 落到同一个桶，就通过链表或红黑树解决哈希冲突。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":126,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"put 流程：\n计算 key 的 hash\n-&gt; 定位数组下标\n-&gt; 桶为空：直接放入\n-&gt; 桶不为空：比较 hash 和 equals\n-&gt; key 已存在：覆盖 value\n-&gt; key 不存在：追加到链表或红黑树\n-&gt; 元素数量超过阈值：触发扩容\"><code>put "},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":78,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 8 之后，桶内元素较少时使用链表；当链表长度达到阈值且数组容量足够大时，会转成红黑树，把极端冲突下的查询复杂度从 O(n) 降到 O(log n)。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：自定义对象作为 key 时必须正确重写 <code>equals()</code> 和 <code>hashCode()</code>；<code>HashMap</code> 本身不是线程安全的，并发写入要使用外部锁或并发容器。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>HashMap</code> 是基于数组、链表和红黑树实现的 key-value 容器。核心思路是先通过 key 的 <code>hashCode()</code> 计算哈希值，再定位到数组桶位；如果多个 key 落到同一个桶，就通过链表或红黑树解决哈希冲突。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":126,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"put 流程：\n计算 key 的 hash\n-&gt; 定位数组下标\n-&gt; 桶为空：直接放入\n-&gt; 桶不为空：比较 hash 和 equals\n-&gt; key 已存在：覆盖 value\n-&gt; key 不存在：追加到链表或红黑树\n-&gt; 元素数量超过阈值：触发扩容\"><code clas"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":78,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 8 之后，桶内元素较少时使用链表；当链表长度达到阈值且数组容量足够大时，会转成红黑树，把极端冲突下的查询复杂度从 O(n) 降到 O(log n)。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：自定义对象作为 key 时必须正确重写 <code>equals()</code> 和 <code>hashCode()</code>；<code>HashMap</code> 本身不是线程安全的，并发写入要使用外部锁或并发容器。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137552790,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"thread-pool-flow","blocks":[{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":51,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>线程池提交任务后，不是直接无限创建线程，而是按照核心线程、任务队列、最大线程、拒绝策略的顺序控制资源。</p>"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满：创建非核心线程\n-&gt; 线程达到最大值且队列仍满：执行拒绝策略\"><code>提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>排查线程池问题时，重点看活跃线程数、队列长度、拒绝次数、任务耗时和下游阻塞情况。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
