"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">Thread\n-&gt; T"},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":11,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>它并不是把数据存在 <code>ThreadLocal</code> 对象里，而是存在当前线程的 <code>ThreadLocalMap</code> 中，<code>ThreadLocal</code> 只是访问这个 Map 的 key。</p>"},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":82,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"try {\n    context.set(userId);\n    // business\n} finally {\n    context.remove();\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-highlighted=\"yes\""},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>所以使用原则很简单：谁设置，谁清理；线程池、Web 请求拦截器、异步任务尤其要放在 <code>finally</code> 中调用 <code>remove()</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137573150,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"class-loading","blocks":[{"label":"class-loading","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":6,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>类加载是 JVM 把 <code>.class</code> 字节码变成运行时 <code>Class</code> 对象的过程。完整过程通常分为加载、验证、准备、解析、初始化，其中验证、准备、解析合称连接。</p>"},{"label":"class-loading","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":84,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"加载：读取 class 字节码\n验证：校验字节码安全性\n准备：为静态变量分配内存并设置默认值\n解析：符号引用转直接引用\n初始化：执行静态变量赋值和 static 代码块\"><code>加载：读取 class 字节码\n验证：校验字节码安全性\n准备：为静态变量分配内存并设置默认值\n解析：符号引用转直接引用\n初始化："},{"label":"class-loading","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":53,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>类加载就是：把 class 搬进 JVM，检查一下，准备静态变量，执行 static 初始化，然后就能用了</p>"},{"label":"class-loading","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":3,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>类初始化通常发生在首次主动使用时，例如 <code>new</code> 对象、访问静态字段、调用静态方法、反射调用等。</p>"},{"label":"class-loading","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><span class=\"em-warn\">双亲委派模型 </span>可以避免核心类被重复或恶意替换，例如应用自定义的 <code>java.lang.String</code> 不应该覆盖 JDK 自带类。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
