{"timestamp":1782137736832,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-jdk-jre","blocks":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp hljs","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137736832,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-jdk-jre","before":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp hljs","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}],"final":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137736833,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"wrapper-cache","blocks":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137736833,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"wrapper-cache","before":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782137736833,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"generics-erasure","blocks":[{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":67,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Java 泛型用于在编译期提供类型约束，减少强制类型转换和运行时类型错误。类型擦除指大部分泛型信息在编译后被擦除为原始类型或边界类型。</p>"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":86,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"List&lt;String&gt; names = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\nnames.add(&quot;ren&quot;);\n\n// 编译后主要保留为 List，泛型约束由编译器检查\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-ja"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":61,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>泛型的价值主要在编译期类型安全。运行期如果需要完整泛型信息，通常要借助匿名子类、反射 Type 或框架提供的类型引用对象。</p>"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":40,"newlineCount":1,"outerSnippet":"<p><pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"List&lt;String&gt; names = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\n\" class=\"\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">List&lt;Stri"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":40,"newlineCount":1,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"List&lt;String&gt; names = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\n\" class=\"\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">List&lt;String&"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":0,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><br></p>"},{"label":"generics-erasure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":0,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p></p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
