JDK 动态代理要求目标类实现接口，底层通过 <code>Proxy</code> 和 <code>InvocationHandler</code> 拦截接口方法调用。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":42,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"interface UserService {\n    void save();\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">interface UserService {\n    void save()"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":192,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"InvocationHandler handler = (proxy, method, args) -&gt; {\n    System.out.println(&quot;before&quot;);\n    Object result = method.invoke(target, args);\n    S"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>通过生成目标类的子类实现代理。不要求接口，但不能代理 <code>final</code> 类和 <code>final</code> 方法。</p>"},{"label":"proxy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":92,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里可以补一句：Spring AOP 默认有接口时倾向使用 JDK 动态代理，没有接口时通常使用 CGLIB。动态代理解决的是“统一横切增强”的问题，不适合把复杂业务逻辑藏进代理层。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138047733,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"hashmap-principle","blocks":[{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>HashMap</code> 是基于数组、链表和红黑树实现的 key-value 容器。核心思路是先通过 key 的 <code>hashCode()</code> 计算哈希值，再定位到数组桶位；如果多个 key 落到同一个桶，就通过链表或红黑树解决哈希冲突。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":126,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"put 流程：\n计算 key 的 hash\n-&gt; 定位数组下标\n-&gt; 桶为空：直接放入\n-&gt; 桶不为空：比较 hash 和 equals\n-&gt; key 已存在：覆盖 value\n-&gt; key 不存在：追加到链表或红黑树\n-&gt; 元素数量超过阈值：触发扩容\"><code>put "},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":78,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 8 之后，桶内元素较少时使用链表；当链表长度达到阈值且数组容量足够大时，会转成红黑树，把极端冲突下的查询复杂度从 O(n) 降到 O(log n)。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：自定义对象作为 key 时必须正确重写 <code>equals()</code> 和 <code>hashCode()</code>；<code>HashMap</code> 本身不是线程安全的，并发写入要使用外部锁或并发容器。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138047734,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"hashmap-principle","before":[{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>HashMap</code> 是基于数组、链表和红黑树实现的 key-value 容器。核心思路是先通过 key 的 <code>hashCode()</code> 计算哈希值，再定位到数组桶位；如果多个 key 落到同一个桶，就通过链表或红黑树解决哈希冲突。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":126,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"put 流程：\n计算 key 的 hash\n-&gt; 定位数组下标\n-&gt; 桶为空：直接放入\n-&gt; 桶不为空：比较 hash 和 equals\n-&gt; key 已存在：覆盖 value\n-&gt; key 不存在：追加到链表或红黑树\n-&gt; 元素数量超过阈值：触发扩容\"><code>put "},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":78,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 8 之后，桶内元素较少时使用链表；当链表长度达到阈值且数组容量足够大时，会转成红黑树，把极端冲突下的查询复杂度从 O(n) 降到 O(log n)。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：自定义对象作为 key 时必须正确重写 <code>equals()</code> 和 <code>hashCode()</code>；<code>HashMap</code> 本身不是线程安全的，并发写入要使用外部锁或并发容器。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>HashMap</code> 是基于数组、链表和红黑树实现的 key-value 容器。核心思路是先通过 key 的 <code>hashCode()</code> 计算哈希值，再定位到数组桶位；如果多个 key 落到同一个桶，就通过链表或红黑树解决哈希冲突。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":126,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"put 流程：\n计算 key 的 hash\n-&gt; 定位数组下标\n-&gt; 桶为空：直接放入\n-&gt; 桶不为空：比较 hash 和 equals\n-&gt; key 已存在：覆盖 value\n-&gt; key 不存在：追加到链表或红黑树\n-&gt; 元素数量超过阈值：触发扩容\"><code clas"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":78,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JDK 8 之后，桶内元素较少时使用链表；当链表长度达到阈值且数组容量足够大时，会转成红黑树，把极端冲突下的查询复杂度从 O(n) 降到 O(log n)。</p>"},{"label":"hashmap-principle","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：自定义对象作为 key 时必须正确重写 <code>equals()</code> 和 <code>hashCode()</code>；<code>HashMap</code> 本身不是线程安全的，并发写入要使用外部锁或并发容器。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138047734,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"thread-pool-flow","blocks":[{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":51,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>线程池提交任务后，不是直接无限创建线程，而是按照核心线程、任务队列、最大线程、拒绝策略的顺序控制资源。</p>"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满：创建非核心线程\n-&gt; 线程达到最大值且队列仍满：执行拒绝策略\"><code>提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>排查线程池问题时，重点看活跃线程数、队列长度、拒绝次数、任务耗时和下游阻塞情况。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138047735,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"thread-pool-flow","before":[{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":51,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>线程池提交任务后，不是直接无限创建线程，而是按照核心线程、任务队列、最大线程、拒绝策略的顺序控制资源。</p>"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满：创建非核心线程\n-&gt; 线程达到最大值且队列仍满：执行拒绝策略\"><code>提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>排查线程池问题时，重点看活跃线程数、队列长度、拒绝次数、任务耗时和下游阻塞情况。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":51,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>线程池提交任务后，不是直接无限创建线程，而是按照核心线程、任务队列、最大线程、拒绝策略的顺序控制资源。</p>"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":79,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-&gt; 队列已满：创建非核心线程\n-&gt; 线程达到最大值且队列仍满：执行拒绝策略\"><code class=\"\">提交任务\n-&gt; 核心线程未满：创建核心线程执行\n-&gt; 核心线程已满：进入任务队列\n-"},{"label":"thread-pool-flow","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>排查线程池问题时，重点看活跃线程数、队列长度、拒绝次数、任务耗时和下游阻塞情况。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138047735,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"threadlocal","blocks":[{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":11,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>ThreadLocal</code> 的作用是让每个线程拥有一份独立变量副本，避免多个线程共享同一个变量。常见场景包括用户上下文、链路追踪traceId、数据库连接等。</p>"},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":61,"newlineCount":2,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Thread\n-&gt; ThreadLocalMap\n-&gt; Entry(ThreadLocal 弱引用, value 强引用)\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">Thread\n-&"},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":11,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>它并不是把数据存在 <code>ThreadLocal</code> 对象里，而是存在当前线程的 <code>ThreadLocalMap</code> 中，<code>ThreadLocal</code> 只是访问这个 Map 的 key。</p>"},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":82,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"try {\n    context.set(userId);\n    // business\n} finally {\n    context.remove();\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted="},{"label":"threadlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>所以使用原则很简单：谁设置，谁清理；线程池、Web 请求拦截器、异步任务尤其要放在 <code>finally</code> 中调用 <code>remove()</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
