{"timestamp":1782138063435,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-jdk-jre","blocks":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp hljs","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138063435,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"jvm-jdk-jre","before":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp hljs","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}],"final":[{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":69,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>JVM、JRE、JDK 是 Java 运行体系的三个层次。JVM 负责执行字节码，JRE 提供运行环境，JDK 提供开发、编译和诊断工具。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":44,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>简单说：运行程序最低需要 JRE，开发程序需要 JDK；JVM 是真正执行字节码的核心。</p>"},{"label":"jvm-jdk-jre","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-cpp","textLen":176,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"JDK\n ├── JRE\n │    ├── JVM\n │    └── Java 核心类库\n └── 开发工具\n      ├── javac // 编译代码\n      ├── jps //查看Java进程\n      ├── jmap//内存分析工具 堆内存 对象分布 可以导出heap dump\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138063436,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"wrapper-cache","blocks":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":39,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"List&lt;String&gt; names = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">List&lt;String&gt; names = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138063436,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"wrapper-cache","before":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":39,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"List&lt;String&gt; names = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">List&lt;String&gt; names = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</"}],"final":[{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>包装类型缓存是 <code>valueOf()</code> 对常用值复用对象，减少频繁创建包装对象。最常见的是 Integer 默认缓存 -128 到 127。</p>"},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java","textLen":154,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"Integer a = 127;\nInteger b = 127;\nInteger c = 128;\nInteger d = 128;\n\nSystem.out.println(a == b); // true，命中缓存\nSystem.out.println(c == d); // false，通常未命中缓存\" "},{"label":"wrapper-cache","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>面试里要强调：缓存是实现优化，不是业务语义。包装类型数值比较优先使用 <code>equals()</code>，但调用前要处理 null。</p>"},{"label"