{"timestamp":1782138094102,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"locks","blocks":[{"label":"locks","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":12,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>synchronized</code> 和 <code>ReentrantLock</code> 都能实现互斥访问，并且都是可重入锁。区别在于：<code>synchronized</code> 是 JVM 关键字，写法简单、自动释放；<code>ReentrantLock</code> 是 JUC 工具类，功能更灵活，但必须手动释放。</p>"},{"label":"locks","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":49,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"\npublic synchronized void method() {\n    // 临界区\n}\" data-code-lang=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\""},{"label":"locks","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-java hljs","textLen":386,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"\nprivate final ReentrantLock lock = new ReentrantLock();\n\npublic void method() {\n    lock.lock();\n    try {\n        // 临界区\n    } finally {\n        lock.unlo"},{"label":"locks","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":12,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>一般优先使用 <code>synchronized</code>。需要尝试加锁、可中断锁、公平锁、多条件队列或复杂同步控制时，再使用 <code>ReentrantLock</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
