","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>执行到 <code>await some_io()</code> 时，若 IO 未完成，当前协程挂起，事件循环去执行其他任务。</p>"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":162,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import asyncio\n\nasync def fetch():\n    await asyncio.sleep(1)\n    return &quot;ok&quot;\n\nasync def main():\n    result = await fetch()\n    print(result)\n\nasy"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":118,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"async def 定义协程函数\n-&gt; 调用后得到协程对象\n-&gt; create_task / await 交给事件循环\n-&gt; await 遇到未完成 IO 时挂起当前协程\n-&gt; 事件循环调度其他协程\n-&gt; IO 完成后恢复原协程继续执行\" data-code-lang=\"pytho"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
