{"timestamp":1782138178044,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","blocks":[{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":37,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>浅拷贝只复制最外层容器，嵌套对象仍共享；深拷贝递归复制所有层级，完全独立。</p>"},{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":132,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import copy\n\na = [[1], [2]]\nb = copy.copy(a)\nc = copy.deepcopy(a)\n\na[0].append(99)\nprint(b)  # [[1, 99], [2]]\nprint(c)  # [[1], [2]]\" data-code-lang=\"python"},{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>不可变对象通常不需要深拷贝；修改嵌套结构且要隔离影响时使用 <code>deepcopy</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
