{"timestamp":1782138178057,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"parameter-passing","blocks":[{"label":"parameter-passing","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":55,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Python 更准确说是“传对象引用”：传递的是对象引用的副本，既不是纯值传递，也不是 C++ 那种引用别名。</p>"},{"label":"parameter-passing","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":157,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def add_item(items):\n    items.append(3)\n\ndef rebind(items):\n    items = [9, 9]\n\na = [1, 2]\nadd_item(a)\nprint(a)  # [1, 2, 3]\nrebind(a)\nprint(a)  # [1, 2, 3"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138178057,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"parameter-passing","before":[{"label":"parameter-passing","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":55,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Python 更准确说是“传对象引用”：传递的是对象引用的副本，既不是纯值传递，也不是 C++ 那种引用别名。</p>"},{"label":"parameter-passing","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":157,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def add_item(items):\n    items.append(3)\n\ndef rebind(items):\n    items = [9, 9]\n\na = [1, 2]\nadd_item(a)\nprint(a)  # [1, 2, 3]\nrebind(a)\nprint(a)  # [1, 2, 3"}],"final":[{"label":"parameter-passing","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":55,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Python 更准确说是“传对象引用”：传递的是对象引用的副本，既不是纯值传递，也不是 C++ 那种引用别名。</p>"},{"label":"parameter-passing","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":157,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def add_item(items):\n    items.append(3)\n\ndef rebind(items):\n    items = [9, 9]\n\na = [1, 2]\nadd_item(a)\nprint(a)  # [1, 2, 3]\nrebind(a)\nprint(a)  # [1, 2, 3"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138178058,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"mro","blocks":[{"label":"mro","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":62,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MRO（Method Resolution Order）是方法解析顺序，决定多继承时 Python 按什么顺序查找父类方法。</p>"},{"label":"mro","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":113,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class A: pass\nclass B(A): pass\nclass C(A): pass\nclass D(B, C): pass\n\nprint(D.mro())  # D -&gt; B -&gt; C -&gt; A -&gt; object\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138178058,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"mro","before":[{"label":"mro","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":62,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MRO（Method Resolution Order）是方法解析顺序，决定多继承时 Python 按什么顺序查找父类方法。</p>"},{"label":"mro","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":113,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class A: pass\nclass B(A): pass\nclass C(A): pass\nclass D(B, C): pass\n\nprint(D.mro())  # D -&gt; B -&gt; C -&gt; A -&gt; object\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code"}],"final":[{"label":"mro","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":62,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MRO（Method Resolution Order）是方法解析顺序，决定多继承时 Python 按什么顺序查找父类方法。</p>"},{"label":"mro","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":113,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class A: pass\nclass B(A): pass\nclass C(A): pass\nclass D(B, C): pass\n\nprint(D.mro())  # D -&gt; B -&gt; C -&gt; A -&gt; object\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
