{"timestamp":1782138179744,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","blocks":[{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":37,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>浅拷贝只复制最外层容器，嵌套对象仍共享；深拷贝递归复制所有层级，完全独立。</p>"},{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":132,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import copy\n\na = [[1], [2]]\nb = copy.copy(a)\nc = copy.deepcopy(a)\n\na[0].append(99)\nprint(b)  # [[1, 99], [2]]\nprint(c)  # [[1], [2]]\" data-code-lang=\"python"},{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>不可变对象通常不需要深拷贝；修改嵌套结构且要隔离影响时使用 <code>deepcopy</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179744,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","before":[{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":37,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>浅拷贝只复制最外层容器，嵌套对象仍共享；深拷贝递归复制所有层级，完全独立。</p>"},{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":132,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import copy\n\na = [[1], [2]]\nb = copy.copy(a)\nc = copy.deepcopy(a)\n\na[0].append(99)\nprint(b)  # [[1, 99], [2]]\nprint(c)  # [[1], [2]]\" data-code-lang=\"python"},{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>不可变对象通常不需要深拷贝；修改嵌套结构且要隔离影响时使用 <code>deepcopy</code>。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":37,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>浅拷贝只复制最外层容器，嵌套对象仍共享；深拷贝递归复制所有层级，完全独立。</p>"},{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":132,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import copy\n\na = [[1], [2]]\nb = copy.copy(a)\nc = copy.deepcopy(a)\n\na[0].append(99)\nprint(b)  # [[1, 99], [2]]\nprint(c)  # [[1], [2]]\" data-code-lang=\"python"},{"label":"deep-copy-shallow-copy","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>不可变对象通常不需要深拷贝；修改嵌套结构且要隔离影响时使用 <code>deepcopy</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179744,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"decorator","blocks":[{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":45,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>装饰器是在不修改原函数代码的前提下，给函数增加日志、鉴权、缓存、计时等横切能力的高阶写法。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>本质是函数接收函数、返回函数。<code>@decorator</code> 等价于 <code>func = decorator(func)</code>。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":212,"newlineCount":11,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from functools import wraps\n\ndef log(func):\n    @wraps(func)\n    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):\n        print(&quot;before&quot;)\n        return func(*args, "},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>建议使用 <code>functools.wraps</code> 保留原函数元信息。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179745,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"decorator","before":[{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":45,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>装饰器是在不修改原函数代码的前提下，给函数增加日志、鉴权、缓存、计时等横切能力的高阶写法。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>本质是函数接收函数、返回函数。<code>@decorator</code> 等价于 <code>func = decorator(func)</code>。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":212,"newlineCount":11,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from functools import wraps\n\ndef log(func):\n    @wraps(func)\n    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):\n        print(&quot;before&quot;)\n        return func(*args, "},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>建议使用 <code>functools.wraps</code> 保留原函数元信息。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":45,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>装饰器是在不修改原函数代码的前提下，给函数增加日志、鉴权、缓存、计时等横切能力的高阶写法。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>本质是函数接收函数、返回函数。<code>@decorator</code> 等价于 <code>func = decorator(func)</code>。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":212,"newlineCount":11,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from functools import wraps\n\ndef log(func):\n    @wraps(func)\n    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):\n        print(&quot;before&quot;)\n        return func(*args, "},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>建议使用 <code>functools.wraps</code> 保留原函数元信息。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
