th\n-&gt; 调用 __enter__\n-&gt; 执行业务代码\n-&gt; 正常或异常退出\n-&gt; 调用 __exit__ 做清理\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">进入"},{"label":"context-manager","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":4,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>with</code> 能保证即使发生异常也会执行清理逻辑。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179747,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"memory-leak","blocks":[{"label":"memory-leak","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":110,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 有自动垃圾回收机制，但如果对象仍然被引用，就不会被释放。\n          内存泄漏本质上通常是：对象已经不再需要，但仍被全局变量、缓存、闭包、任务或第三方库持有。\n        </p>"},{"label":"memory-leak","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":211,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"观察进程 RSS / Python heap / 对象数量是否持续增长\n      -&gt; 用 tracemalloc 对比内存快照\n      -&gt; 用 gc 查看不可达对象和引用关系\n      -&gt; 检查全局变量、缓存、闭包、回调、后台任务\n      -&gt; 检查异常日志、trace"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179747,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"memory-leak","before":[{"label":"memory-leak","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":110,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 有自动垃圾回收机制，但如果对象仍然被引用，就不会被释放。\n          内存泄漏本质上通常是：对象已经不再需要，但仍被全局变量、缓存、闭包、任务或第三方库持有。\n        </p>"},{"label":"memory-leak","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":211,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"观察进程 RSS / Python heap / 对象数量是否持续增长\n      -&gt; 用 tracemalloc 对比内存快照\n      -&gt; 用 gc 查看不可达对象和引用关系\n      -&gt; 检查全局变量、缓存、闭包、回调、后台任务\n      -&gt; 检查异常日志、trace"}],"final":[{"label":"memory-leak","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":110,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 有自动垃圾回收机制，但如果对象仍然被引用，就不会被释放。\n          内存泄漏本质上通常是：对象已经不再需要，但仍被全局变量、缓存、闭包、任务或第三方库持有。\n        </p>"},{"label":"memory-leak","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":211,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"观察进程 RSS / Python heap / 对象数量是否持续增长\n      -&gt; 用 tracemalloc 对比内存快照\n      -&gt; 用 gc 查看不可达对象和引用关系\n      -&gt; 检查全局变量、缓存、闭包、回调、后台任务\n      -&gt; 检查异常日志、trace"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179748,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"python-del","blocks":[{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          <code>__del__</code> 是 Python 中的析构方法，当对象即将被销毁时，\n          Python 会尝试自动调用该方法。它通常用于对象销毁前的收尾逻辑。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":243,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n          def __init__(self, name):\n              self.name = name\n              print(f&quot;{self.name} 创建了&quot;)\n      \n          def __del_"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          需要注意的是，<code>del u</code> 删除的是变量 <code>u</code> 对对象的引用，\n          并不一定代表对象会立即销毁。只有当对象没有其他引用时，才可能触发\n          <code>__del__</code>。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          实际开发中，不建议依赖 <code>__del__</code> 释放文件、数据库连接、\n          HTTP 连接等资源，更推荐使用 <code>with</code> 上下文管理器或显式\n          <code>close()</code> 方法。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":239,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"# 推荐：使用 with 自动释放资源\n      with open(&quot;data.txt&quot;, &quot;r&quot;) as f:\n          data = f.read()\n      \n      \n      # 推荐：使用 try...finally 显式关闭连接\n  "},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          面试中可以总结为：<code>__del__</code> 是对象销毁前自动调用的析构方法，\n          但由于执行时机不稳定，生产环境中不应依赖它管理关键资源。\n          文件、连接、锁等资源更适合通过 <code>with</code> 或 <code>close()</code> 主动释放。\n        </p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179748,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"python-del","before":[{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          <code>__del__</code> 是 Python 中的析构方法，当对象即将被销毁时，\n          Python 会尝试自动调用该方法。它通常用于对象销毁前的收尾逻辑。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":243,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n          def __init__(self, name):\n              self.name = name\n              print(f&quot;{self.name} 创建了&quot;)\n      \n          def __del_"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          需要注意的是，<code>del u</code> 删除的是变量 <code>u</code> 对对象的引用，\n          并不一定代表对象会立即销毁。只有当对象没有其他引用时，才可能触发\n          <code>__del__</code>。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          实际开发中，不建议依赖 <code>__del__</code> 释放文件、数据库连接、\n          HTTP 连接等资源，更推荐使用 <code>with</code> 上下文管理器或显式\n          <code>close()</code> 方法。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":239,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"# 推荐：使用 with 自动释放资源\n      with open(&quot;data.txt&quot;, &quot;r&quot;) as f:\n          data = f.read()\n      \n      \n      # 推荐：使用 try...finally 显式关闭连接\n  "},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          面试中可以总结为：<code>__del__</code> 是对象销毁前自动调用的析构方法，\n          但由于执行时机不稳定，生产环境中不应依赖它管理关键资源。\n          文件、连接、锁等资源更适合通过 <code>with</code> 或 <code>close()</code> 主动释放。\n        </p>"}],"final":[{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          <code>__del__</code> 是 Python 中的析构方法，当对象即将被销毁时，\n          Python 会尝试自动调用该方法。它通常用于对象销毁前的收尾逻辑。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":243,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n          def __init__(self, name):\n              self.name = name\n              print(f&quot;{self.name} 创建了&quot;)\n      \n          def __del_"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          需要注意的是，<code>del u</code> 删除的是变量 <code>u</code> 对对象的引用，\n          并不一定代表对象会立即销毁。只有当对象没有其他引用时，才可能触发\n          <code>__del__</code>。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          实际开发中，不建议依赖 <code>__del__</code> 释放文件、数据库连接、\n          HTTP 连接等资源，更推荐使用 <code>with</code> 上下文管理器或显式\n          <code>close()</code> 方法。\n        </p>"},{"label":"python-del","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":239,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"# 推荐：使用 with 自动释放资源\n      with open(&quot;data.txt&quot;, &quot;r&quot;) as f:\n          data = f.read()\n      \n      \n      # 推荐：使用 try...finally 显式关闭连接\n  "},{"label":"python-del","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          面试中可以总结为：<code>__del__</code> 是对象销毁前自动调用的析构方法，\n          但由于执行时机不稳定，生产环境中不应依赖它管理关键资源。\n          文件、连接、锁等资源更适合通过 <code>with</code> 或 <code>close()</code> 主动释放。\n        </p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179749,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"wsgi-asgi","blocks":[{"label":"wsgi-asgi","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          WSGI 全称是 <code>Web Server Gateway Interface</code>，\n          ASGI 全称是 <code>Asynchronous Server Gateway Interface</code>。\n          它们都是 Python Web 应用和 Web 服务器之间的接口规范。\n        </p>"},{"label":"wsgi-asgi","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":13,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          WSGI 是同步接口，主要用于传统 HTTP 请求；\n          ASGI 是异步接口，支持 <code>async / await</code>，\n          更适合 WebSocket、SSE、长连接和高并发 IO 场景。\n        </p>"},{"label":"wsgi-asgi","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":106,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"浏览器请求\n        -&gt; Nginx / Web Server\n        -&gt; WSGI / ASGI Server\n        -&gt; Python Web 框架\n        -&gt; 业务代码\"><code class=\"\">浏览器请求\n        -&gt; N"},{"label":"wsgi-asgi","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":13,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          WSGI 是 Python 传统同步 Web 服务接口规范，适合普通 HTTP 请求；\n          ASGI 是面向异步场景的接口规范，支持 <code>async / await</code>，\n          可以处理 WebSocket、SSE、长连接等场景。\n          FastAPI 通常基于 ASGI 运行，Flask 传统模式通常基于 "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
