{"timestamp":1782138179758,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"metaclass","blocks":[{"label":"metaclass","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":4,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>元类是“类的类”。普通类默认由 <code>type</code> 创建，元类可以控制类的创建过程。</p>"},{"label":"metaclass","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":110,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n    pass\n\nprint(type(User))      # &lt;class 'type'&gt;\nprint(type(User()))    # &lt;class '__main__.User'&gt;\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code cl"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179759,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"metaclass","before":[{"label":"metaclass","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":4,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>元类是“类的类”。普通类默认由 <code>type</code> 创建，元类可以控制类的创建过程。</p>"},{"label":"metaclass","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":110,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n    pass\n\nprint(type(User))      # &lt;class 'type'&gt;\nprint(type(User()))    # &lt;class '__main__.User'&gt;\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code cl"}],"final":[{"label":"metaclass","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":4,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>元类是“类的类”。普通类默认由 <code>type</code> 创建，元类可以控制类的创建过程。</p>"},{"label":"metaclass","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":110,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n    pass\n\nprint(type(User))      # &lt;class 'type'&gt;\nprint(type(User()))    # &lt;class '__main__.User'&gt;\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code cl"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138179759,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"property-decorator","blocks":[{"label":"property-decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>property</code> 把方法包装成属性访问形式，可配合 getter、setter、deleter 做校验和封装。</p>"},{"label":"property-decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":267,"newlineCount":12,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n    def __init__(self, age):\n        self._age = age\n\n    @property\n    def age(self):\n        return self._age\n\n    @age.setter\n    def age(sel"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
