{"timestamp":1782138179761,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"exception-handling","blocks":[{"label":"exception-handling","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":6,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Python 使用异常传递错误，从调用栈向上传播，直到被匹配的 <code>except</code> 捕获或终止程序。</p>"},{"label":"exception-handling","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":122,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"try:\n    result = 10 / x\nexcept ZeroDivisionError:\n    result = 0\nelse:\n    print(&quot;success&quot;)\nfinally:\n    print(&quot;cleanup&quot;)\" data-code-la"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
