{"timestamp":1782138188669,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"context-manager","blocks":[{"label":"context-manager","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":4,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>上下文管理器配合 <code>with</code> 使用，进入时调用 <code>__enter__</code>，退出时调用 <code>__exit__</code>，保证资源释放。</p>"},{"label":"context-manager","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":71,"newlineCount":1,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"with open(&quot;demo.txt&quot;, &quot;w&quot;, encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;) as f:\n    f.write(&quot;hello&quot;)\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"langua"},{"label":"context-manager","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":63,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"进入 with\n-&gt; 调用 __enter__\n-&gt; 执行业务代码\n-&gt; 正常或异常退出\n-&gt; 调用 __exit__ 做清理\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python hljs\" data-highlighted=\"ye"},{"label":"context-manager","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":4,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>with</code> 能保证即使发生异常也会执行清理逻辑。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
