assName":"","codeClass":"","textLen":106,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"浏览器请求\n        -&gt; Nginx / Web Server\n        -&gt; WSGI / ASGI Server\n        -&gt; Python Web 框架\n        -&gt; 业务代码\"><code class=\"\">浏览器请求\n        -&gt; N"},{"label":"wsgi-asgi","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":13,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          WSGI 是 Python 传统同步 Web 服务接口规范，适合普通 HTTP 请求；\n          ASGI 是面向异步场景的接口规范，支持 <code>async / await</code>，\n          可以处理 WebSocket、SSE、长连接等场景。\n          FastAPI 通常基于 ASGI 运行，Flask 传统模式通常基于 "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138188673,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"closure","blocks":[{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":101,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          闭包是指：内部函数引用了外部函数中的变量，并且这个内部函数被返回到外部继续使用。\n          即使外部函数已经执行结束，被引用的外部变量仍然会被保留下来。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":20,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"闭包 = 函数 + 被函数捕获的外部变量\"><code class=\"\">闭包 = 函数 + 被函数捕获的外部变量</code></pre>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":278,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def counter():\n          count = 0\n      \n          def add():\n              nonlocal count\n              count += 1\n              return count\n      \n     "},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          这里的 <code>count</code> 没有定义成全局变量，\n          但每次调用 <code>c()</code> 时都能记住上一次的值。\n          这说明闭包可以让函数保存自己的状态。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 闭包和 Go 闭包本质上是同一个概念，\n          都是函数捕获外部作用域中的变量，并在外部函数结束后继续使用这些变量。\n          区别主要在语法上：Python 修改外层变量需要使用 <code>nonlocal</code>，\n          Go 的匿名函数可以直接修改外层变量。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":122,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 闭包是指内部函数引用外部函数的变量，并且内部函数被返回后仍然可以访问这些变量。\n          它的核心是函数能够记住创建它时的上下文，常用于装饰器、回调函数、状态封装和延迟执行等场景。\n        </p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138188673,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"closure","before":[{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":101,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          闭包是指：内部函数引用了外部函数中的变量，并且这个内部函数被返回到外部继续使用。\n          即使外部函数已经执行结束，被引用的外部变量仍然会被保留下来。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":20,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"闭包 = 函数 + 被函数捕获的外部变量\"><code class=\"\">闭包 = 函数 + 被函数捕获的外部变量</code></pre>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":278,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def counter():\n          count = 0\n      \n          def add():\n              nonlocal count\n              count += 1\n              return count\n      \n     "},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          这里的 <code>count</code> 没有定义成全局变量，\n          但每次调用 <code>c()</code> 时都能记住上一次的值。\n          这说明闭包可以让函数保存自己的状态。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 闭包和 Go 闭包本质上是同一个概念，\n          都是函数捕获外部作用域中的变量，并在外部函数结束后继续使用这些变量。\n          区别主要在语法上：Python 修改外层变量需要使用 <code>nonlocal</code>，\n          Go 的匿名函数可以直接修改外层变量。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":122,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 闭包是指内部函数引用外部函数的变量，并且内部函数被返回后仍然可以访问这些变量。\n          它的核心是函数能够记住创建它时的上下文，常用于装饰器、回调函数、状态封装和延迟执行等场景。\n        </p>"}],"final":[{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":101,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          闭包是指：内部函数引用了外部函数中的变量，并且这个内部函数被返回到外部继续使用。\n          即使外部函数已经执行结束，被引用的外部变量仍然会被保留下来。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":20,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"闭包 = 函数 + 被函数捕获的外部变量\"><code class=\"\">闭包 = 函数 + 被函数捕获的外部变量</code></pre>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":278,"newlineCount":15,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def counter():\n          count = 0\n      \n          def add():\n              nonlocal count\n              count += 1\n              return count\n      \n     "},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          这里的 <code>count</code> 没有定义成全局变量，\n          但每次调用 <code>c()</code> 时都能记住上一次的值。\n          这说明闭包可以让函数保存自己的状态。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 闭包和 Go 闭包本质上是同一个概念，\n          都是函数捕获外部作用域中的变量，并在外部函数结束后继续使用这些变量。\n          区别主要在语法上：Python 修改外层变量需要使用 <code>nonlocal</code>，\n          Go 的匿名函数可以直接修改外层变量。\n        </p>"},{"label":"closure","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":122,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Python 闭包是指内部函数引用外部函数的变量，并且内部函数被返回后仍然可以访问这些变量。\n          它的核心是函数能够记住创建它时的上下文，常用于装饰器、回调函数、状态封装和延迟执行等场景。\n        </p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138188674,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"nonlocal","blocks":[{"label":"nonlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>nonlocal</code> 用于在内层函数中修改外层非全局变量。没有它时，赋值会被视为创建局部变量，可能触发 <code>UnboundLocalError</code>。</p>"},{"label":"nonlocal","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":128,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def make_counter():\n    count = 0\n\n    def add():\n        nonlocal count\n        count += 1\n        return count\n\n    return add\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><c"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138188674,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"nonlocal","before":[{"label":"nonlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>nonlocal</code> 用于在内层函数中修改外层非全局变量。没有它时，赋值会被视为创建局部变量，可能触发 <code>UnboundLocalError</code>。</p>"},{"label":"nonlocal","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":128,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def make_counter():\n    count = 0\n\n    def add():\n        nonlocal count\n        count += 1\n        return count\n\n    return add\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><c"}],"final":[{"label":"nonlocal","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>nonlocal</code> 用于在内层函数中修改外层非全局变量。没有它时，赋值会被视为创建局部变量，可能触发 <code>UnboundLocalError</code>。</p>"},{"label":"nonlocal","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":128,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"def make_counter():\n    count = 0\n\n    def add():\n        nonlocal count\n        count += 1\n        return count\n\n    return add\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><c"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138188675,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"pydantic","blocks":[{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":153,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Pydantic 是 Python 中常用的<strong>数据校验和数据解析工具</strong>，\n          主要用于解决“外部数据结构不可靠”的问题。\n          它可以基于类型注解，对接口参数、配置项、JSON 数据和大模型输出进行类型校验、类型转换、必填校验和默认值处理。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          <code>BaseModel</code> 是 Pydantic 的核心，用来定义数据结构，并自动完成字段校验、类型转换和默认值处理。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":213,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel\n      \n      class User(BaseModel):\n          name: str\n          age: int\n          is_active: bool = True\n      \n      user"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          <code>Field</code> 用于设置字段限制，例如长度、范围、默认值和描述信息。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":216,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel, Field\n      \n      class Product(BaseModel):\n          name: str = Field(min_length=2, max_length=50)\n          price: float"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Pydantic v2 常用 <code>field_validator</code> 和 <code>model_validator</code>，\n          分别用于单字段校验和多字段联合校验。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":332,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel, field_validator\n      \n      class UserRegister(BaseModel):\n          username: str\n      \n          @field_validator(&quot;"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":107,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          在 AI Agent / RAG 项目中，Pydantic 常用于校验大模型返回的 JSON 结构，\n          避免字段缺失、类型错误或格式不稳定导致后续流程异常。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":244,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel\n      from typing import List\n      \n      class LLMAnswer(BaseModel):\n          answer: str\n          confidence: float\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
