{"timestamp":1782138188679,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"mutable-immutable","blocks":[{"label":"mutable-immutable","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":40,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>可变对象创建后内容可原地修改；不可变对象一旦创建，任何“修改”都会绑定到新对象。</p>"},{"label":"mutable-immutable","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":82,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"nums = [1, 2]\nnums.append(3)      # 原地修改\n\ns = &quot;ab&quot;\ns = s + &quot;c&quot;         # 绑定到新字符串对象\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python"},{"label":"mutable-immutable","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>函数默认参数不要直接使用可变对象，避免共享同一默认实例。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
