{"timestamp":1782138212132,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"asyncio-timeout-cancel","blocks":[{"label":"asyncio-timeout-cancel","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>协程超时和取消需要显式处理，避免任务泄漏和异常被吞掉。常用 <code>asyncio.wait_for</code>、<code>asyncio.timeout</code>、<code>Task.cancel()</code>。</p>"},{"label":"asyncio-timeout-cancel","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":136,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"try:\n    result = await asyncio.wait_for(fetch(), timeout=3)\nexcept asyncio.TimeoutError:\n    result = None\nfinally:\n    await cleanup()\" data-code-lang=\"py"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138212133,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"asyncio-timeout-cancel","before":[{"label":"asyncio-timeout-cancel","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>协程超时和取消需要显式处理，避免任务泄漏和异常被吞掉。常用 <code>asyncio.wait_for</code>、<code>asyncio.timeout</code>、<code>Task.cancel()</code>。</p>"},{"label":"asyncio-timeout-cancel","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":136,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"try:\n    result = await asyncio.wait_for(fetch(), timeout=3)\nexcept asyncio.TimeoutError:\n    result = None\nfinally:\n    await cleanup()\" data-code-lang=\"py"}],"final":[{"label":"asyncio-timeout-cancel","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":16,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>协程超时和取消需要显式处理，避免任务泄漏和异常被吞掉。常用 <code>asyncio.wait_for</code>、<code>asyncio.timeout</code>、<code>Task.cancel()</code>。</p>"},{"label":"asyncio-timeout-cancel","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":136,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"try:\n    result = await asyncio.wait_for(fetch(), timeout=3)\nexcept asyncio.TimeoutError:\n    result = None\nfinally:\n    await cleanup()\" data-code-lang=\"py"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
