{"timestamp":1782138433704,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"async-await","before":[{"label":"async-await","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":13,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>async / await</code> 是 Python 协程语法糖，基于单线程事件循环，在 IO 等待时切换任务。</p>"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"事件循环 + 协程 + 非阻塞 IO + 主动让出执行权\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python hljs\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">事件循环 + 协程 + 非阻塞 IO + 主动让出执行权</code></pre>"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>执行到 <code>await some_io()</code> 时，若 IO 未完成，当前协程挂起，事件循环去执行其他任务。</p>"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":162,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import asyncio\n\nasync def fetch():\n    await asyncio.sleep(1)\n    return &quot;ok&quot;\n\nasync def main():\n    result = await fetch()\n    print(result)\n\nasy"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":118,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"async def 定义协程函数\n-&gt; 调用后得到协程对象\n-&gt; create_task / await 交给事件循环\n-&gt; await 遇到未完成 IO 时挂起当前协程\n-&gt; 事件循环调度其他协程\n-&gt; IO 完成后恢复原协程继续执行\" data-code-lang=\"pytho"}],"final":[{"label":"async-await","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":13,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>async / await</code> 是 Python 协程语法糖，基于单线程事件循环，在 IO 等待时切换任务。</p>"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"事件循环 + 协程 + 非阻塞 IO + 主动让出执行权\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\" data-highlighted=\"yes\">事件循环 + 协程 + 非阻塞 IO + 主动让出执行权</code></pre>"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>执行到 <code>await some_io()</code> 时，若 IO 未完成，当前协程挂起，事件循环去执行其他任务。</p>"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":162,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import asyncio\n\nasync def fetch():\n    await asyncio.sleep(1)\n    return &quot;ok&quot;\n\nasync def main():\n    result = await fetch()\n    print(result)\n\nasy"},{"label":"async-await","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":118,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"async def 定义协程函数\n-&gt; 调用后得到协程对象\n-&gt; create_task / await 交给事件循环\n-&gt; await 遇到未完成 IO 时挂起当前协程\n-&gt; 事件循环调度其他协程\n-&gt; IO 完成后恢复原协程继续执行\" data-code-lang=\"pytho"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138433702,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"concurrency","blocks":[{"label":"concurrency","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":55,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>三种并发模型解决不同问题：多线程适合 IO 密集，多进程适合 CPU 密集，协程适合高并发 IO 且成本更低。</p>"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用 <code>threading</code>，同一进程内多线程共享内存。适合网络请求、文件读写等 IO 场景，线程等待 IO 时会释放 GIL。</p>"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":102,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import threading\n\ndef task():\n    print(&quot;hello&quot;)\n\nt = threading.Thread(target=task)\nt.start()\nt.join()\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"langu"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":24,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>注意线程安全问题，共享可变状态需要锁或原子操作。</p>"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用 <code>multiprocessing</code>，每个进程有独立内存和 GIL，可真正并行利用多核 CPU。</p>"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":112,"newlineCount":7,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from multiprocessing import Process\n\ndef task():\n    print(&quot;hello&quot;)\n\np = Process(target=task)\np.start()\np.join()\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code cl"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>进程间通信成本更高，常用 Queue、Pipe 等方式。</p>"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":7,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>使用 <code>asyncio</code> 和 <code>async / await</code>，在单线程事件循环中切换，遇到 <code>await</code> 时让出执行权。</p>"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":99,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import asyncio\n\nasync def task():\n    await asyncio.sleep(1)\n    print(&quot;done&quot;)\n\nasyncio.run(task())\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":28,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>协程切换成本低，但不适合长时间占用 CPU 的同步代码。</p>"},{"label":"concurrency","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":41,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>口诀：CPU 密集优先多进程，阻塞 IO 可用多线程，高并发异步 IO 优先协程。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
