{"timestamp":1782138433706,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"decorator","blocks":[{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":45,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>装饰器是在不修改原函数代码的前提下，给函数增加日志、鉴权、缓存、计时等横切能力的高阶写法。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>本质是函数接收函数、返回函数。<code>@decorator</code> 等价于 <code>func = decorator(func)</code>。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":212,"newlineCount":11,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from functools import wraps\n\ndef log(func):\n    @wraps(func)\n    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):\n        print(&quot;before&quot;)\n        return func(*args, "},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>建议使用 <code>functools.wraps</code> 保留原函数元信息。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138433707,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"decorator","before":[{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":45,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>装饰器是在不修改原函数代码的前提下，给函数增加日志、鉴权、缓存、计时等横切能力的高阶写法。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>本质是函数接收函数、返回函数。<code>@decorator</code> 等价于 <code>func = decorator(func)</code>。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":212,"newlineCount":11,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from functools import wraps\n\ndef log(func):\n    @wraps(func)\n    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):\n        print(&quot;before&quot;)\n        return func(*args, "},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>建议使用 <code>functools.wraps</code> 保留原函数元信息。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":45,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>装饰器是在不修改原函数代码的前提下，给函数增加日志、鉴权、缓存、计时等横切能力的高阶写法。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>本质是函数接收函数、返回函数。<code>@decorator</code> 等价于 <code>func = decorator(func)</code>。</p>"},{"label":"decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":212,"newlineCount":11,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from functools import wraps\n\ndef log(func):\n    @wraps(func)\n    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):\n        print(&quot;before&quot;)\n        return func(*args, "},{"label":"decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>建议使用 <code>functools.wraps</code> 保留原函数元信息。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
