n      \n      class UserRegister(BaseModel):\n          username: str\n      \n          @field_validator(&quot;"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":107,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          在 AI Agent / RAG 项目中，Pydantic 常用于校验大模型返回的 JSON 结构，\n          避免字段缺失、类型错误或格式不稳定导致后续流程异常。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":244,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel\n      from typing import List\n      \n      class LLMAnswer(BaseModel):\n          answer: str\n          confidence: float\n    "}],"final":[{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":153,"newlineCount":4,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Pydantic 是 Python 中常用的<strong>数据校验和数据解析工具</strong>，\n          主要用于解决“外部数据结构不可靠”的问题。\n          它可以基于类型注解，对接口参数、配置项、JSON 数据和大模型输出进行类型校验、类型转换、必填校验和默认值处理。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          <code>BaseModel</code> 是 Pydantic 的核心，用来定义数据结构，并自动完成字段校验、类型转换和默认值处理。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":213,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel\n      \n      class User(BaseModel):\n          name: str\n          age: int\n          is_active: bool = True\n      \n      user"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":5,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          <code>Field</code> 用于设置字段限制，例如长度、范围、默认值和描述信息。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":216,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel, Field\n      \n      class Product(BaseModel):\n          name: str = Field(min_length=2, max_length=50)\n          price: float"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          Pydantic v2 常用 <code>field_validator</code> 和 <code>model_validator</code>，\n          分别用于单字段校验和多字段联合校验。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":332,"newlineCount":10,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel, field_validator\n      \n      class UserRegister(BaseModel):\n          username: str\n      \n          @field_validator(&quot;"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":107,"newlineCount":3,"outerSnippet":"<p>\n          在 AI Agent / RAG 项目中，Pydantic 常用于校验大模型返回的 JSON 结构，\n          避免字段缺失、类型错误或格式不稳定导致后续流程异常。\n        </p>"},{"label":"pydantic","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":244,"newlineCount":8,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from pydantic import BaseModel\n      from typing import List\n      \n      class LLMAnswer(BaseModel):\n          answer: str\n          confidence: float\n    "}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138433714,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"coroutine","blocks":[{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Python 协程是一种可暂停和恢复的函数，通过 <code>async def</code> 定义，用 <code>await</code> 等待 IO 并让出执行权。</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":39,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>协程不是操作系统线程，适合高并发 IO 场景；不适合直接承担 CPU 密集计算</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":58,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>线程是操作系统管理的 切换时需要保存和恢复寄存器、程序计数器、栈指针等上下文，成本较高; 协程主要是程序自己管理的。</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":56,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>但协程底层的网络 IO、文件 IO 仍然需要操作系统支持，只是协程之间的调度切换不像线程那样依赖内核线程调度。 </p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":99,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import asyncio\n\nasync def fetch():\n    await asyncio.sleep(1)\n    return &quot;ok&quot;\n\nasyncio.run(fetch())\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138433715,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"coroutine","before":[{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Python 协程是一种可暂停和恢复的函数，通过 <code>async def</code> 定义，用 <code>await</code> 等待 IO 并让出执行权。</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":39,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>协程不是操作系统线程，适合高并发 IO 场景；不适合直接承担 CPU 密集计算</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":58,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>线程是操作系统管理的 切换时需要保存和恢复寄存器、程序计数器、栈指针等上下文，成本较高; 协程主要是程序自己管理的。</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":56,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>但协程底层的网络 IO、文件 IO 仍然需要操作系统支持，只是协程之间的调度切换不像线程那样依赖内核线程调度。 </p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":99,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import asyncio\n\nasync def fetch():\n    await asyncio.sleep(1)\n    return &quot;ok&quot;\n\nasyncio.run(fetch())\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language"}],"final":[{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>Python 协程是一种可暂停和恢复的函数，通过 <code>async def</code> 定义，用 <code>await</code> 等待 IO 并让出执行权。</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":39,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>协程不是操作系统线程，适合高并发 IO 场景；不适合直接承担 CPU 密集计算</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":58,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>线程是操作系统管理的 切换时需要保存和恢复寄存器、程序计数器、栈指针等上下文，成本较高; 协程主要是程序自己管理的。</p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":56,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>但协程底层的网络 IO、文件 IO 仍然需要操作系统支持，只是协程之间的调度切换不像线程那样依赖内核线程调度。 </p>"},{"label":"coroutine","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":99,"newlineCount":6,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"import asyncio\n\nasync def fetch():\n    await asyncio.sleep(1)\n    return &quot;ok&quot;\n\nasyncio.run(fetch())\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><code class=\"language"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
