{"timestamp":1782138452410,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"multiprocessing","blocks":[{"label":"multiprocessing","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":15,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>multiprocessing</code> 通过 <strong>多进程</strong> 绕过 GIL。</p>"},{"label":"multiprocessing","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":51,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>GIL 是 CPython 解释器进程级别的锁。每个子进程有自己的解释器和 GIL，因此可以并行执行。</p>"},{"label":"multiprocessing","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":70,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"线程 1、线程 2、线程 3\n共享同一个进程的 GIL\n\n进程 1 有自己的 GIL\n进程 2 有自己的 GIL\n进程 3 有自己的 GIL\"><code>线程 1、线程 2、线程 3\n共享同一个进程的 GIL\n\n进程 1 有自己的 GIL\n进程 2 有自己的 GIL\n进程 3 有自己的 GIL</code><"},{"label":"multiprocessing","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":23,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>因此多进程可以真正利用多核 CPU 并行执行。</p>"},{"label":"multiprocessing","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":29,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>多进程适合“算得重、通信少”的任务，不适合频繁共享大状态。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
