{"timestamp":1782138452431,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"property-decorator","blocks":[{"label":"property-decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>property</code> 把方法包装成属性访问形式，可配合 getter、setter、deleter 做校验和封装。</p>"},{"label":"property-decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":267,"newlineCount":12,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n    def __init__(self, age):\n        self._age = age\n\n    @property\n    def age(self):\n        return self._age\n\n    @age.setter\n    def age(sel"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138452432,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"property-decorator","before":[{"label":"property-decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>property</code> 把方法包装成属性访问形式，可配合 getter、setter、deleter 做校验和封装。</p>"},{"label":"property-decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":267,"newlineCount":12,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n    def __init__(self, age):\n        self._age = age\n\n    @property\n    def age(self):\n        return self._age\n\n    @age.setter\n    def age(sel"}],"final":[{"label":"property-decorator","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":8,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>property</code> 把方法包装成属性访问形式，可配合 getter、setter、deleter 做校验和封装。</p>"},{"label":"property-decorator","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python","textLen":267,"newlineCount":12,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"class User:\n    def __init__(self, age):\n        self._age = age\n\n    @property\n    def age(self):\n        return self._age\n\n    @age.setter\n    def age(sel"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782138452432,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"dataclass","blocks":[{"label":"dataclass","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":9,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p><code>dataclass</code> 适合定义以数据为主的类，自动生成 <code>__init__</code>、<code>__repr__</code>、<code>__eq__</code> 等样板代码。</p>"},{"label":"dataclass","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"language-python hljs","textLen":128,"newlineCount":5,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"from dataclasses import dataclass, field\n\n@dataclass\nclass User:\n    name: str\n    tags: list[str] = field(default_factory=list)\" data-code-lang=\"python\"><c"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
