{"timestamp":1782204641302,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"MCP-Registry","blocks":[{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":75,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MCP Server 不由中心注册表统一登记，而是由 <strong>Client 在本地配置中声明</strong>，启动时按配置拉起或连接 Server，完成握手后纳入可用工具池。</p>"},{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":340,"newlineCount":13,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"// Cursor: .cursor/mcp.json 示例\n{\n  &quot;mcpServers&quot;: {\n    &quot;filesystem&quot;: {\n      &quot;command&quot;: &quot;npx&quot;,\n      &quot;args&quot"},{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>连接建立后 Client 发 <code>initialize</code>，双方交换 capabilities，再拉取 <code>tools/list</code> 完成「注册」。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782204641303,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:final","message":"save pipeline final state","data":{"sectionId":"MCP-Registry","before":[{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":75,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MCP Server 不由中心注册表统一登记，而是由 <strong>Client 在本地配置中声明</strong>，启动时按配置拉起或连接 Server，完成握手后纳入可用工具池。</p>"},{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":340,"newlineCount":13,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"// Cursor: .cursor/mcp.json 示例\n{\n  &quot;mcpServers&quot;: {\n    &quot;filesystem&quot;: {\n      &quot;command&quot;: &quot;npx&quot;,\n      &quot;args&quot"},{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>连接建立后 Client 发 <code>initialize</code>，双方交换 capabilities，再拉取 <code>tools/list</code> 完成「注册」。</p>"}],"final":[{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":75,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MCP Server 不由中心注册表统一登记，而是由 <strong>Client 在本地配置中声明</strong>，启动时按配置拉起或连接 Server，完成握手后纳入可用工具池。</p>"},{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":340,"newlineCount":13,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"// Cursor: .cursor/mcp.json 示例\n{\n  &quot;mcpServers&quot;: {\n    &quot;filesystem&quot;: {\n      &quot;command&quot;: &quot;npx&quot;,\n      &quot;args&quot"},{"label":"MCP-Registry","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>连接建立后 Client 发 <code>initialize</code>，双方交换 capabilities，再拉取 <code>tools/list</code> 完成「注册」。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
{"timestamp":1782204641304,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"Model-Context-Protocol","blocks":[{"label":"Model-Context-Protocol","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":86,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>底层统一采用 <strong>JSON-RPC 2.0</strong> 消息格式，通过不同 <strong>Transport</strong> 承载；同一连接上可发 request、response、notification 三类消息。</p>"},{"label":"Model-Context-Protocol","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":175,"newlineCount":9,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"// tools/call 请求示例\n{\n  &quot;jsonrpc&quot;: &quot;2.0&quot;,\n  &quot;id&quot;: 2,\n  &quot;method&quot;: &quot;tools/call&quot;,\n  &quot;params&quot;: {\n    "},{"label":"Model-Context-Protocol","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MCP 管「Client ↔ Server」通道；模型侧的 Tool Calling 管「LLM 选哪个工具、填什么参」，Client 负责把模型输出映射为 <code>tools/call</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
