{"timestamp":1782204641304,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"MCP-schema","blocks":[{"label":"MCP-schema","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":4,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MCP 工具在 Server 中声明 <code>name</code>、<code>description</code>、<code>inputSchema</code> 三要素；<code>inputSchema</code> 为标准 <strong>JSON Schema</strong>，描述参数类型、必填项与约束，经 <code>tools/list</code> 暴露给 Clie"},{"label":"MCP-schema","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":538,"newlineCount":26,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"// Server 侧工具定义（逻辑结构）\n{\n  &quot;name&quot;: &quot;search_docs&quot;,\n  &quot;description&quot;: &quot;搜索企业知识库文档&quot;,\n  &quot;inputSchema&quot;: {\n    &quo"},{"label":"MCP-schema","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":11,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>写好 schema 的关键：<code>description</code> 写清业务语义；<code>required</code> 标必填；用 <code>enum</code> / <code>minimum</code> 约束取值；Server 执行前再做一次 schema 校验，防止模型幻觉参数。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
