{"timestamp":1782204647649,"sessionId":"ce29c0","location":"content-editor.js:savePage:before-repair","message":"blocks before repair","data":{"sectionId":"Model-Context-Protocol","blocks":[{"label":"Model-Context-Protocol","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":86,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>底层统一采用 <strong>JSON-RPC 2.0</strong> 消息格式，通过不同 <strong>Transport</strong> 承载；同一连接上可发 request、response、notification 三类消息。</p>"},{"label":"Model-Context-Protocol","tag":"PRE","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":175,"newlineCount":9,"outerSnippet":"<pre contenteditable=\"false\" data-raw-code=\"// tools/call 请求示例\n{\n  &quot;jsonrpc&quot;: &quot;2.0&quot;,\n  &quot;id&quot;: 2,\n  &quot;method&quot;: &quot;tools/call&quot;,\n  &quot;params&quot;: {\n    "},{"label":"Model-Context-Protocol","tag":"P","className":"","codeClass":"","textLen":10,"newlineCount":0,"outerSnippet":"<p>MCP 管「Client ↔ Server」通道；模型侧的 Tool Calling 管「LLM 选哪个工具、填什么参」，Client 负责把模型输出映射为 <code>tools/call</code>。</p>"}]},"hypothesisId":"A,E","runId":"post-fix"}
